                     <interp inst="t18260216-137-person901" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live with Mr. Wadmore, a pawnbroker. On the 27th of January I took in the two pillows, two sheets, and a table cloth, from the female prisoner - I had not seen her before, but I know she is the person.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260216-137-person902">
